Nabisco Brands Ltd, 80 pct-owned by RJRNabisco Inc &lt;RJR>, said it named president R. Edward Glover aschief executive, replacing J.R. MacDonald, who remains asvice-chairman and chairman of the executive committee,effective immediately.    Glover has been president and chief operating officer sinceApril, 1986, Nabisco said. Reuter&#3;